{"tid":2147325,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[重溫] 匯豐銀行就洗錢認罰19億美元","createTime":"2020-08-09T07:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T10:04:58.000Z","uid":65789,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8cf1ef8286c05d21ca99399c8fb75cd572e35268","tid":2147325,"uid":65789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.bbc.com/staticarchive/882dd001d36914d8613d1ce2fa6e127674195dc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fstaticarchive%2F882dd001d36914d8613d1ce2fa6e127674195dc7.jpg&h=9a140e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來自美國的報道稱，匯豐銀行同意就為伊朗洗錢問題向美國當局繳納19億美元的高額和解金。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">這是歷來此類案件中涉及的最高金額。</span><br />\n<br />\n匯豐銀行同意繳納罰款意味著該銀行將不必面臨美國的司法起訴。<br />\n<br />\n據信美國當局可能將在星期二（12月11日）宣佈這一進展。<br />\n<br />\n美國檢控官指責匯豐銀行通過美國金融系統為伊朗當局以及墨西哥販毒集團洗錢。<br />\n<br />\n匯豐銀行此前承認銀行內部對洗錢行為的控制存在疏漏，上個月還宣佈預留15億美元以備繳納和解金或罰金。<br />\n<br />\n而就在星期一，英國渣打銀行業同意支付3.27億美元，就美聯儲指控其違反美國對伊朗、利比亞和緬甸的制裁與美國方面達成和解。<br />\n<br />\n渣打銀行今年8月已向美國監管機構支付了3.4億美元。<br />\n<br />\n觀察人士指出，美國以及紐約州當局近來顯著加緊了對洗錢活動以及違反制裁行為的打擊力度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2012/12/121211_hsbc_us.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld%2F2012%2F12%2F121211_hsbc_us.shtml&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminL4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=8702ddfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld%2F2012%2F12%2F121211_hsbc_us.shtml&h=232aa366\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2012/12/121211_hsbc_us.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"976fea3b41a6bb9c170ab37924a99b0fb68d4f53","tid":2147325,"uid":120791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476f373af181574ae6cb55f7aa7e7196cca7d07a","tid":2147325,"uid":65789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d35b127abdb84b5cf879f2ea788f4791bf99501","tid":2147325,"uid":193969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2TF8jn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2TF8jn.png&h=7b484c5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59e005d374349190ee564fa23dd9254880bca145","tid":2147325,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:48:57.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啲管理層當股東傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b390dd62c8663332fd9b0f82e066602b9a224801","tid":2147325,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d35b127abdb84b5cf879f2ea788f4791bf99501","tid":2147325,"uid":193969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2TF8jn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2TF8jn.png&h=7b484c5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T08:01:42.000Z","msg":"[重溫］"},{"pid":"d8da42846d540e16eab3190af8943d251b0bc944","tid":2147325,"uid":97078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T08:39:21.000Z","msg":"買港銀股票風險咁高 重有無人會買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c8f2126a7bcd888c16747ac22f667fb5032628","tid":2147325,"uid":120791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T10:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ea456da98f2a38738bf9b395f1a51576584884","tid":2147325,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"好想王冬勝企硬出聲明死攬林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/d